    "htmlObj": "%3Ch3%20id%3D%22ef4fb2a5519086cb6f4539ef5cf32b06f%22%20data-placeholder%3D%22Type%20or%20paste%20your%20content%20here!%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happens%20behind%20the%20smile%20you%20see%20at%20your%20table%3F%20A%20story%20of%20turbulence%2C%20trauma%2C%20and%20quiet%20triumph.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99ve%20ever%20sat%20at%20a%20restaurant%20and%20felt%20taken%20care%20of%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20the%20story%20behind%20that%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EAnd%20if%20you%E2%80%99ve%20ever%20thought%20hospitality%20was%20just%20about%20carrying%20plates%20or%20pouring%20wine%2C%20let%20Usama%20show%20you%20the%20truth%20that%20lives%20behind%20the%20scenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EBecause%20this%20is%20not%20just%20his%20story.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20story%20of%20thousands%20who%20serve%20you%20without%20being%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EWhen%20we%20first%20spoke%2C%20Usama%20Farrukh%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pitch%20himself.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to.%20He%20simply%20told%20the%20truth.%20Gently.%20Honestly.%20Almost%20like%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20much%20it%20mattered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20knew%20%E2%80%94%20we%20had%20to%20begin%20with%20him.%20Because%20in%20a%20world%20that%20celebrates%20loud%20wins%2C%20Usama%20is%20a%20quiet%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20quiet%20soul%20growing%20up%20in%20a%20small%20city%2C%20surrounded%20by%20the%20noise%20and%20warmth%20of%20a%20slightly%20dysfunctional%20joint%20family.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20belong%20%E2%80%94%20like%20I%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20elsewhere%2C%20doing%20something%20different.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EUsama%20grew%20up%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20India%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%E2%80%9Cresponsible%20eldest%20son%2C%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20head%20boy%20badge%20and%20a%20head%20full%20of%20quiet%20questions.%20His%20father%20was%20a%20doctor.%20The%20plan%20was%20to%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20dad's%20a%20doctor%2C%20but%20I%20always%20knew%20that%20path%20wasn't%20for%20me.%20Not%20because%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20admire%20it%20%E2%80%94%20I%20did%20%E2%80%94%20but%20because%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20see%20myself%20in%20that%20role.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EAnd%20then%20came%20the%20airport%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20a%20turning%20point%20that%20shaped%20everything.%20Usama%20was%20dropping%20off%20his%20uncle%20at%20the%20Lucknow%20airport.%20As%20they%20waited%2C%20he%20noticed%20an%20Air%20India%20747%20parked%20on%20the%20tarmac.%20A%20massive%2C%20gleaming%20aircraft%20that%20looked%20almost%20otherworldly.%20And%20then%20he%20saw%20them%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Jet%20Airways%20cabin%20crew%2C%20walking%20with%20elegance%2C%20confidence%2C%20and%20quiet%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20looked%20like%20something%20out%20of%20a%20movie.%20In%20that%20moment%2C%20it%20hit%20me%20like%20a%20wave.%20I%20told%20myself%3A%20%E2%80%98This%E2%80%A6%20this%20is%20what%20I%20want%20to%20do.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EThat%20dream%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20romantic.%20It%20was%20survival.%20Usama%20borrowed%20Rs%201.63%20lakh%20for%20his%20aviation%20diploma%2C%20vowing%20to%20pay%20it%20back.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20Jet%20Airways%E2%80%99%20height%20requirement.%20But%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop.%20He%20joined%20IndiGo%20as%20ground%20staff%20member.%20Then%20Officer%20Security.%20Then%20came%20Air%20India%20Express.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EAnd%20then%20%E2%80%94%20flight%20%2318.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CA%20passenger%20collapsed.%20I%20had%20to%20perform%20CPR.%20We%20were%20thousands%20of%20feet%20in%20the%20air%20%E2%80%94%20no%20doctors%2C%20no%20hospitals.%20Just