ed%20the%20team%2C%20and%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20opening%20for%20dinner.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EAnd%20they%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EThis%20is%20hospitality.%20The%20part%20no%20guest%20sees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EUsama%20remembers%20it%20all%20%E2%80%94%20the%20mirror%20moments%2C%20the%20overlooked%20hours%2C%20the%20praise%20that%20never%20came.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20give%20everything%E2%80%A6%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20seen%20as%20doing%20your%20job.%20But%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20show%20up%20for%20praise.%20I%20show%20up%20because%20it%20matters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EHe%20remembers%20the%20guest%20who%20had%20just%20come%20from%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20felt%20normal%20again.%E2%80%99%20That%20moment%20stays%20with%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EAnd%20yes%2C%20the%20smile%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20fake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20smile%20didn%E2%80%99t%20hide%20the%20pain%20%E2%80%94%20it%20carried%20me%20through%20the%20madness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EUsama%20is%20the%20manager%20who%20steps%20onto%20the%20floor%20when%20others%20hide%20in%20the%20office.%20Who%20still%20remembers%20what%20it%20means%20to%20wipe%20tables%2C%20lift%20trays%2C%20reset%20cutlery%20%E2%80%94%20even%20after%2018-hour%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20this%20industry%20needs%20to%20hear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22p1%22%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99re%20a%20guest%20%E2%80%94%20remember%2C%20the%20person%20behind%20the%20smile%20is%20carrying%20more%20than%20just%20your%20plates.%20If%20you%E2%80%99re%20in%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20you%20are%20not%20invisible.%20If%20you%E2%80%99re%20building%20teams%20%E2%80%94