    "htmlObj": "%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A22px%3B%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20flunked%20engineering.%20I%20served%20tables.%20I%20built%20a%20movement.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20the%20story%20behind%20Humans%20of%20Hospitality.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20any%20of%20this%20%E2%80%94%20before%20London%2C%20before%20Megan%E2%80%99s%2C%20before%20HoH%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20just%20a%20kid%20in%20India%20trying%20to%20outrun%20his%20own%20report%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20bunk%20classes.%20Not%20occasionally%20%E2%80%94%20like%20clockwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFailed%20engineering%20two%20years%20straight.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20dropped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20said%20I%20had%20no%20direction.%20And%20honestly%3F%20They%20weren%E2%80%99t%20wrong.z%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20switched%20to%20Computer%20Science.%20Still%20had%20as%20many%20backlogs%20as%20subjects.%20But%20I%20pushed%20through.%20Four%20years%20later%2C%20I%20had%20a%20BSc%20degree%20in%20my%20hand%E2%80%A6%20and%20no%20job%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20COVID%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20campus%20placements.%20No%20interviews.%20Just%20me%2C%20my%20parents%E2%80%99%20living%20room%2C%20and%20a%20sinking%20feeling%20that%20maybe%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20anywhere%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20give%20up%20on%20myself.%20Not%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20did%20what%20felt%20like%20the%20only%20step%20forward%20%E2%80%94%20I%20applied%20for%20a%20Master%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20landed%20in%20London%20with%20one%20suitcase%2C%20no%20winter%20jacket%2C%20and%20a%20quiet%20promise%20to%20myself%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMake%20it%20count.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20International%20Business%20Management%20%E2%80%94%20specialisation%20in%20strategy%2C%20entrepreneurship%2C%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20words.%20Big%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20reality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20was%20attending%